         ("The Honest Take", "<p>Warrington is the higher-ranked, more affordable option with broader career outcomes. Herbert is the pick for candidates specifically targeting Miami, Latin American business, or South Florida real estate. For Florida residents, Warrington's in-state tuition makes it one of the best values in the state.</p>"),
